<li id="cite_note-137"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-137">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text">Cornuelle, <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://archive.today/20080630041355/http://www.derafsh-kaviyani.com/english/sassanian.html">An Overview of the Sassanian Persian Military</a>; Sidnell (2006), 273</span>
